    {
      "label": "Content description",
      "value": "Recto: The letter starts with opening greetings (l. 2) suggesting not much is missing from the beginning of the letter. The sender refers to a purchase of textile from Merv for six coins (l. 4) and asks the addressee, Ab\u016b Mu\u1e25ammad, to make haste with what he asked him to do (l. 7). The letter ends with blessings for the addressee."
